 HOST HARDWARE LAYER\n705 |                     </span>\n706 |                     <div className=\"text-white/40 text-left mb-2\">Unsecured Host hypervisor Memory Space (Host-OS)</div>\n707 |                     <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-3\">\n708 |                       <div className=\"border border-[#009DFF]/30 bg-[#009DFF]/5 p-3.5 rounded-lg relative space-y-2 group hover:border-[#009DFF] transition-all\">\n709 |                         <div className=\"absolute top-2 right-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-ping\" />\n710 |                         <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold block text-[9.5px]\">INTEL SGX</span>\n711 |                         <div className=\"text-[8.5px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">\n712 |                           Isolated User-Space Enclave. Memory fully encrypted at silicon layer.\n713 |                         </div>\n714 |                         <div className=\"text-[7.5px] text-[#009DFF] font-semibold bg-[#009DFF]/10 px-1 rounded uppercase tracking-wider py-0.5 inline-block\">\n715 |                           SEALED PARTITION\n716 |                         </div>\n717 |                       </div>\n718 |                       <div className=\"border border-emerald-500/30 bg-emerald-500/5 p-3.5 rounded-lg relative space-y-2 group hover:border-emerald-500 transition-all\">\n719 |                         <div className=\"absolute top-2 right-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-ping\" />\n720 |                         <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold block text-[9.5px]\">AMD SEV-SNP</span>\n721 |                         <div className=\"text-[8.5px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">\n722 |                           Secure Nested Paging. Strict hardware CPU isolation and register lock.\n723 |                         </div>\n724 |                         <div className=\"text-[7.5px] text-emerald-400 font-semibold bg-emerald-500/10 px-1 rounded uppercase tracking-wider py-0.5 inline-block\">\n725 |                           ATTESTATION ACTIVE\n726 |                         </div>\n727 |                       </div>\n728 |                     </div>\n729 |                     <div className=\"border border-white/5 bg-black/60 p-2.5 mt-4 rounded text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-2\">\n730 |                       <Lock className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n731 |                       <span className=\"text-white/60\">\n732 |                         CONTINUOUS ZERO-KNOWLEDGE LOG TELEMETRY: <strong className=\"text-white\">ACTIVE</strong>\n733 |                       </span>\n734 |                     </div>\n735 |                   </div>\n736 |                 </div>\n737 |               </div>\n738 |             </WorkspaceCard>\n739 | \n740 | \n741 | \n742 |             <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n743 |               <WorkspaceCard className=\"space-y-3 p-4\">\n744 |                 <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] tracking-wider uppercase block\">Hardware Specs</span>\n745 |                 <h4 className=\"text-[12.5px] font-bold text-white font-mono\">Sovereign Cluster Node Specs</h4>\n746 |                 <ul className=\"space-y-2 font-mono text-[10.5px] text-white/50\">\n747 |                   <li className=\"flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n748 |                     <span>Cluster Enclave Type:</span>\n749 |                     <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">EPYC™ Dual 64-Core</span>\n750 |                   </li>\n751 |                   <li className=\"flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n752 |                     <span>Memory Encryption:</span>\n753 |                     <span className=\"text-white\">AES-128-XTS Hardware Engine</span>\n754 |                   </li>\n755 |                   <li className=\"flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n756 |                     <span>Root Cert Key:</span>\n757 |                     <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-semibold\">2048-bit HSM signed</span>\n758 |                   </li>\n759 |                   <li className=\"flex justify-between\">\n760 |                     <span>Isolation Scale:</span>\n761 |                     <span className=\"text-white\">Complete Decoupling</span>\n762 |                   </li>\n763 |                 </ul>\n764 |               </WorkspaceCard>\n765 | \n766 |               <WorkspaceCard className=\"space-y-3 p-4\">\n767 |                 <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-emerald-400 tracking-wider uppercase block\">Attestation Ledger</span>\n768 |                 <h4 className=\"text-[12.5px] font-bold text-white font-mono\">silicon-level verification</h4>\n769 |                 <ul className=\"space-y-2 font-mono text-[10.5px] text-white/50\">\n770 |                   <li className=\"flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n771 |                     <span>Attestation State:</span>\n772 |                     <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold uppercase\">PASSED (Verified)</span>\n773 |                   </li>\n774 |                   <li className=\"flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n775 |                     <span>Validation Authority:</span>\n776 |                     <span className=\"text-white\">GFF Sovereign HSM</span>\n777 |                   </li>\n778 |                   <li className=\"flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n779 |                     <span>Cert Fingerprint:</span>\n780 |                     <span className=\"text-white font-mono text-[9px] truncate max-w-[120px]\">0xAFE991BC8841BEE8</span>\n781 |                   </li>\n782 |                   <li className=\"flex justify-between\">\n783 |                     <span>Audit Interval:</span>\n784 |                     <span className=\"text-white\">Every 3600 Cycles</span>\n785 |                   </li>\n786 |  