xt-[14px]\">NO AI OPERATIONS ENROLLED</h4>\n        <p className=\"text-white/50 text-[11px] leading-relaxed\">This client partition currently has no active or archived sandboxed runtime records in the registry.</p>\n      </div>\n    </WorkspaceCard>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
