ing Log Display**\n\nI'm now focusing on the log display within the `WorkspaceCard` component, specifically the rendering of `agent.logs`. I'm going through lines 638 to 658, and evaluating the use of the `font-mono`, the color-coding based on log content (REBOOT, CRITICAL, Attestation, etc.), and the overall structure. I'm aiming for more effective formatting and readability for these critical logs. I'm also considering alternative strategies to show the logs in a cleaner, more readable layout.\n\n\n**Improving Button Structure**\n\nI am now focusing on the 'RECYCLE CORE' button within the `WorkspaceCard`, specifically the conditional rendering tied to `isRebooting`. I'm evaluating the button's layout (line 634-648), considering replacing the inline `flex-grow` with a more concise method. Also, I am looking to simplify the conditional logic for the spinning refresh icon and text to ensure a smoother transition during rebooting. I want to refine the styling and responsiveness.\n\n\n"}}
